description:
Free Video Converter

Convertilla is a simple and convenient program for converting video and music files between various formats. It supports MP4, FLV, MKV, MPG, AVI, MOV, WMV, M4V, 3GP, MP3, WEBM, OPUS, AAC, FLAC, APE, WAV, ASF. We prepared presets for the following devices: Android, iOS (iPhone, iPad), Windows Phone, iPod, Blackberry, Sony PSP and PS3, Microsoft XBOX 360 and Zune, Chrome OS, Ubuntu, Tizen, Nokia N-series and others.
- Added ability to convert folders;
- Added ability to convert DVDs;
- Added progress indication on top of the program icon;
- Improved format support;
- Bug fixes.
